Capabilities & Scope

Supervised classification of Iris species (e.g., Iris-setosa, Iris-versicolor, Iris-virginica).

Zero external services; all computation is local.

Command-line interface for single-record scoring.

Reusable Python functions for programmatic use (data loading, model training, inference). 

KNN Predictor

